    public static class BuildRuleEvent.StartedRuleKeyCalc
extends BuildRuleEvent.Started
implements RuleKeyCalculationEvent.Started
    Marks the start of processing a rule to calculate its rule key. We overload this as both a rule start and rule key calc start event to generate less events and be more efficient.
